<!--<h4>First Side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>sādhāraṇa saṁvatsara pusya śu 7 budha vā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rāmu taḷkaṁṭidēvi <unclear>pūjāri</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> jiyya <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yala pōlajiyya<unclear>lu</unclear> bācejiyya 
<lb n="4"/><unclear>tīgala</unclear> taḷajīyala viḍimuḍi be 
<lb n="5"/>ṭṭi vritti muccenānu vijjenānu 
<lb n="6"/>biḍa biḍataramu sarigānu 
<lb n="7"/>paṁci kuḍuvagalavāru vīra 
<lb n="8"/>la Ubhayānmatini saṁgaya 
<lb n="9"/>batteni vrālu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="10"/>Ubhayānumati 
<lb n="11"/>daṁḍlūri vī <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> rāju koḍuku vī 
<lb n="12"/>rarāju koḍuku boṁmarāju <unclear>sā</unclear> 
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>kṣulu</unclear> 
</p>

